# Agent scope — simulation, engineering, life sciences, Studio UI

**Not in scope here:** `li-httpd`, `httpd-plan-loop.py`, tier5 HTTP, MCP gateway — those run in a **separate** process/plan (`2026-05-16-li-httpd-plan.md`).

## Canonical plans

| Area | Document |
|------|----------|
| Studio + profiles + UX | `docs/game-dev/world-studio-vision.md`, `PH-world-studio-program.md` |
| Algorithms / verticals | `docs/ecosystem/algorithms-and-libraries-plan.md` |
