| Correctness policy | `li-benchmark-correctness.mdc`, `benchmarks/harness/reference.py` |

## Philosophy

- **Correct per published spec, as fast as possible** — not “match C++/Python bit-for-bit.”
- **Small + large goldens**; cross-lang checks are sanity only.
- **DCE allowed only when verified** (harness spec + magnitude/time guards).

## Packages (adjacent libraries)

`packages/li-physics-*`, `li-sim-*`, `li-chem*`, `li-scene`, `li-ui`, `li-math` — extend with tests and goldens; do not fold studio into `compiler/`.
